{
  "text": "In this paper, we propose a pipeline for integrating automatic assessment, i.e. detectors of student traits, directly into the tutoring system. We validate our approach for the case of developmental dyscalculia (DD) (a specific learning disability a\u21b5ecting the acquisition of arithmetic skills [CITATION_1] ) and the game-based training environment Calcularis [CITATION_2] .",
